Name: athena-cyrus-imap-client
Summary: The Cyrus IMAP client utilities and libraries, for Athena.
License: CMU/Freely Distributable
Group: System Environment/Libraries

Requires: athena-cyrus-sasl athena-perl

%description
The Cyrus IMAP (Internet Message Access Protocol) client utilities
and libraries are part of the Cyrus IMAP server distribution, from
Carnegie Mellon University.  Cyrus IMAP software provides access to
personal mail and system-wide bulletin boards through the IMAP
protocol.
